{"tid":1583138,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【920死線，未FC】香港又送錢比大陸","createTime":"2019-09-20T12:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T13:46:56.000Z","uid":92277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f2bc3e817db63fba9433f1749733098cf0d4df53","tid":1583138,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:41:49.000Z","msg":"歡迎轉發，我唔是作者：<br />\n<br />\n告急🌠今日💥9月20號到期啦！政府又要送錢上大陸<br />\n香港電力能自給自足！澳門用大陸電，打風大停電<br />\n一波未停，一波又起！<br />\n<br />\n💀 政府趁亂，打算偷偷通過議案，用超高價向大陸買電，將香港儲備滙走！<br />\n事實上，香港用電從來不缺！本地電商亦能解問題！<br />\n（一）反對用香港公帑去幫大陸內地經濟填債！<br />\n（二）反對陰乾香港，架空香港能源自主性！<br />\n<br />\n#公眾咨詢期就快過 #記得快d填表 #藍絲黃絲聯手阻止林鄭偷錢<br />\n👉 馬上按入: <a href=\"https://www.susdev.org.hk/tc/vcf.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.susdev.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fvcf.php&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG1xdyOQTk4RMct2Rsqyof94c%3D&h=1e35474f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.susdev.org.hk/tc/vcf.php</a><br />\n<br />\n提示:<br />\n<br />\n⛔<span style=\"color: red;\">問題3: 選擇 「不支持」，</span>以拒絕中國借口「巴黎協定」而強逼香港支持興建核電廠等「清潔但高危」的電力投資！<br />\n⛔<span style=\"color: red;\">問題10:  填上類似「反對向香港以外地方購買電力和食水等設施</span>」自己作為佳，重覆怕佢當一個。<br />\n<br />\n⚠其他問題: 如沒意見，可留空不填。<br />\n<br />\n#香港人真係好忙<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2204332393027294?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2204332393027294%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG1xdyOQTk4RMct2Rsqyof94c%3D&h=a207328d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2204332393027294?sfns=mo</a><br />\n請廣傳"},{"pid":"2a2117df492829a021811e69f293d36220c23ccd","tid":1583138,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:42:09.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"21a92f0f8c96aab9f967a5720ef51887714f1d5f","tid":1583138,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:42:21.000Z","msg":"香港人真係好撚忙"},{"pid":"efe598e9a2081602e0704a5a96a2ff6cfaba3e84","tid":1583138,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:42:29.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊 - 會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人 - 食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG1xdyOQTk4RMct2Rsqyof94c%3D&h=4179df04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"9e9a10d22cb0ad00126bf65bdbf31cabc9dfddc1","tid":1583138,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:42:46.000Z","msg":"大家聽日記得留番係屋企好好地抖下"},{"pid":"eae40d19395df9bc64602836406c7a355cf2a210","tid":1583138,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:43:13.000Z","msg":"政府借減碳排放為名，話要向中國買電<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」詻詢<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日截止</span></span><br />\n快啲將你既意見SEND EMAIL去：  comments@susdev.org.hk<br />\n<br />\n✏參考意見✏<br />\n<br />\n致可持續發展委員會成員：<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」諮詢中，當局建議以「 更緊密的區域合作」向中國購買零排放電力，然而本港電力穩定度遠高於中國南方電網，擔心向中國買電會帶來電力不穩，影響本港金融、航運、交通、以至市民日常生活。<br />\n此外，《巴黎協定》為一些面積小、欠缺天然資源的小島嶼發展中國家(Small Island Developing States,SIDS) 如新加坡、斐濟等，可因應它們特殊情況，制訂關於溫室氣體低排放發展的策略。<br />\n由於香港地少人多，局限可再生能源發展，亦缺乏天然資源，可選擇的減排策略有限，與其他小島嶼發展中國家情況面臨同樣的挑戰。<br />\n就此本人有以下意見：<br />\n一. 聯網供電會損害供電穩定，故此反對進一步向中國買電，反對採取更緊密的區域合作，香港應以本地發電為主，確保電力穩定；<br />\n二. 遵照2014年未來發電燃料組合諮詢，增加本地天然氣發電及可再生能源比例，代替區域聯網；<br />\n三. 爭取香港以地區名義，直接向政府間氣候變化專門委員會(IPCC)匯報減排策略；<br />\n四. 爭取以發展中國家/地區(Small Island Developing States) 名義，因應香港的情況，以更彈性的方式履行《巴黎協定》；<br />\n五. 放緩人口增長，收緊移民政策，減低整體耗電量；<br />\n六. 制訂具體香港再工業化政策，加強本港農業及回收業的支援，減少貨物入口時的碳排放。"},{"pid":"89e08b96eb1572474e91d2099bf672b7f5ffb541","tid":1583138,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:44:45.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"2f824896e7f9481a92c565a404bdceb93d1cc172","tid":1583138,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89e08b96eb1572474e91d2099bf672b7f5ffb541","tid":1583138,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:44:45.000Z","msg":"推呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:45:49.000Z","msg":"唔好填表，直接send email過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37650edb1422ac0bffec59f4cb1059fda4d2fd70","tid":1583138,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f824896e7f9481a92c565a404bdceb93d1cc172","tid":1583138,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89e08b96eb1572474e91d2099bf672b7f5ffb541","tid":1583138,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:44:45.000Z","msg":"推呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:45:49.000Z","msg":"唔好填表，直接send email過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:46:41.000Z","msg":"驚人太長唔肯做<br />\n然後copy template 又話會當一份"},{"pid":"00d7aae807785545f2d0ace612455a9c335b70db","tid":1583138,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37650edb1422ac0bffec59f4cb1059fda4d2fd70","tid":1583138,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f824896e7f9481a92c565a404bdceb93d1cc172","tid":1583138,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89e08b96eb1572474e91d2099bf672b7f5ffb541","tid":1583138,"uid":92277,"like"